<plot>Tired of making choices and cynical of their omnipresence, Guy (John Gregory Willard) struggles to move in the face of fate when confronted with two choices that could fulfill or devastate his life. "Chance Encounter" is the rare instance of seeing two outcomes at once as Guy searches for purpose in an world of uncertainty.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?099419</url></doc>
